OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will be cloudy with
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells. Showers will
OL,7,Fbe isolated and mostly in the west at
OL,8,Ffirst. These showers spread north and
OL,9,Feast from early afternoon before
OL,10,Fclearing in the south towards the
OL,11,Fevening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear spells with a few
OL,14,Fshowers at first, these mainly in the
OL,15,Fnorth. Then dry, becoming cloudy with
OL,16,Frain in the west and the south later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
