OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FBright spells, dry north and
OL,6,Feast at first. Cloudy with widespread
OL,7,Fand heavy rain in the west and south
OL,8,Fat first, this spreading northeast
OL,9,Ffrom the early afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,12,FOutbreaks of heavy rain pass northeast
OL,13,Fduring Sunday. This will be followed
OL,14,Fby bright or sunny spells and showers
OL,15,Fthrough the rest of the period.
OL,16,FEastern parts stay mostly dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
